"application>, använd menyalternativet <menuchoice><guimenu>Redigera</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Kontrollera enheten med LanguageTool</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> eller använd genvägen <keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></"
"keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information, please refer to <ulink url=\"https://languagetool.org/"
